SchemaItem.Name: 00010_Convert_SettingsData
SchemaItem.M01:
-- ============================================= -- Declare and using an UPDATE cursor -- ============================================= DECLARE @view int, @id uniqueidentifier, @profileId uniqueidentifier, @panelId uniqueidentifier
DECLARE settings_cursor CURSOR FOR SELECT DefaultView, Id, ProfileId, FormPanelId FROM AsapFormPanelConfig WHERE SettingsData IS NULL FOR UPDATE of SettingsData
DECLARE @count smallint SELECT @count = 1
OPEN settings_cursor FETCH NEXT FROM settings_cursor INTO @view, @id, @profileId, @panelId
WHILE (@@fetch_status <> -1) BEGIN IF (@@fetch_status <> -2) BEGIN -- ============================================= -- Declare and using a READ_ONLY cursor -- ============================================= DECLARE columns_cursor CURSOR READ_ONLY FOR SELECT ColumnName, ColumnWidth, IsHidden FROM AsapPanelColumnConfig WHERE PanelId = @panelId AND ProfileId = @profileId ORDER BY Position
DECLARE @columnSettings varchar(8000) SET @columnSettings = '' DECLARE @columnName nvarchar(300) DECLARE @columnWidth int DECLARE @isHidden bit OPEN columns_cursor
FETCH NEXT FROM columns_cursor INTO @columnName, @columnWidth, @isHidden WHILE (@@fetch_status <> -1) BEGIN IF (@@fetch_status <> -2) BEGIN set @columnSettings = @columnSettings + '<column property="' + @columnName + '" isHidden="' + (case @isHidden when 0 then 'false' else 'true' end) + '" width="' + cast(@columnWidth as varchar(20)) + '" />' END FETCH NEXT FROM columns_cursor INTO @columnName, @columnWidth, @isHidden END
CLOSE columns_cursor DEALLOCATE columns_cursor
UPDATE AsapFormPanelConfig SET SettingsData = '<Configuration><defaultView><view id="' + cast(@view as varchar(2)) + '"/></defaultView><columnWidths>' + @columnSettings + '</columnWidths></Configuration>' WHERE Id = @Id END FETCH NEXT FROM settings_cursor INTO @view, @id, @profileId, @panelId SELECT @count = @count + 1 END
CLOSE settings_cursor DEALLOCATE settings_cursor
